The dataset used in this project was provided as part of my Machine Learning internship at 
FlyRank for educational and analytical purposes.

It contains anonymized SEO performance metrics for webpages, including search volume, impressions, 
click-through rate (CTR), average search position, content type, and trend-related features.

The analysis presented in this repository is my first week project and was conducted to practice exploratory
data analysis (EDA), statistical analysis, and data visualization using Python.
